      About this item

      • Hybrid ANC and Be Aware Mode: Hybrid Active Noise Cancelation leverages mics on the exterior and interior of the headphone for optimal noise cancelation performance across a broad frequency range. Activate the Hybrid Active Noise Canceling to eliminate external distractions up to 30 dB or switch to Be Aware mode to remain connected to your environment.
      • Cloud Foam Comfort: Form-Fit Earcups are ergonomically shaped to the natural outline of the ear. The 1 Cloud Foam cushions and adjustable hinges further customize your comfort for any travel, workout, or commute.
      • Customize Your Sound + Experience via JLab App: With the new JLab App, customize the ANC/Be Aware settings, touch controls, and sound to your personal preference - or use the presets for JLab Signature, Balance or Bass Boost. Safe hearing option allows you to protect your ears from hearing damage with volume limits. Plus, get software updates for your product right when they're available. Available on the App Store or Google Play Store.
      • Crystal Clear Calls: Furnished with cutting-edge noise-canceling microphones, these headphones ensure crystal clear and uninterrupted communication during calls, ensuring exceptional clarity and eliminating external disturbances for an impeccable conversation experience.
      • Easy Connections + Google Find My: Utilize Bluetooth Multipoint to seamlessly connect to and toggle between two devices simultaneously for added convenience. Wireless Share Mode allows you to share audio wirelessly between two Lux headphones.
      • Easy Connections: Utilize Bluetooth Multipoint to seamlessly connect to and toggle between two devices simultaneously for added convenience. Wireless Share Mode allows you to share audio wirelessly between two Lux headphones. Plus effortless pairing with an Android device with Google Fast Pair and Microsoft Swift Pair. When you take out your headphones and have a supported Android device, youll see a pop-up enabling you to connect via Bluetooth. With Microsoft Swift Pair, seamlessly connect to Microsoft Windows 10 and 11 devices. When a Windows 10 or 11 PC detects the Go Lux ANC it will prompt you to connect with a single click.
      • Google Find My Device: With Google Find My Device, you can locate your headphones.
      • Includes: Headphones, Charging Cable, JLab 2 Year Warranty

        Go Lux ANC on-ear headphones

        Merchant Video

        1. Immersive Lab Quality Sound


          Enjoy exceptional sound quality via 40mm drivers, bringing deep bass and clarity to your music.

          With 70+ hours of playtime (40+ hours with ANC on), enjoy uninterrupted music sessions or calls.

        2. Hybrid ANC and Be Aware Mode


          Hybrid Active Noise Cancelation leverages mics on the exterior and interior of the headphone for optimal noise cancelation performance across a broad frequency range. Activate the Hybrid Active Noise Canceling to eliminate external distractions up to 30 dB or switch to Be Aware mode to remain connected to your environment.

        3. Cloud Foam Comfort


          Form-Fit Earcups are ergonomically shaped to the natural outline of the ear. The 1 Cloud Foam cushions and adjustable hinges further customize your comfort for any travel, workout, or commute.

        4. Customize Your Sound + Experience via JLab App


          With the new JLab App, customize the ANC/Be Aware settings, touch controls, and sound to your personal preference - or use the presets for JLab Signature, Balance or Bass Boost. Safe hearing option allows you to protect your ears from hearing damage with volume limits. Plus, get software updates for your product right when they're available.

          Available on the App Store or Google Play Store.

        5. Crystal Clear Calls


          Furnished with cutting-edge noise-canceling microphones, these headphones ensure crystal clear and uninterrupted communication during calls, ensuring exceptional clarity and eliminating external disturbances for an impeccable conversation experience.

        6. Easy Connections + Google Find My


          Utilize Bluetooth Multipoint to seamlessly connect to and toggle between two devices simultaneously for added convenience. Wireless Share Mode allows you to share audio wirelessly between two Lux headphones. Plus effortless pairing with an Android device with Google Fast Pair and Microsoft Swift Pair.

        Built-in Lab Spatial Audio

        Featuring spatial audio EQ straight from the Lab, enjoy another dimension and immersive sound. JLabs spatial audio algorithm makes you feel like youre sitting in the middle of a concert or standing in the middle of a fight scene.

        How customer reviews and ratings work

        Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

        To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

        • Millenwagon
          5.0 out of 5 stars DOWNLOAD THE APP AND USE THE EQ
          Reviewed in the United Kingdom on April 26, 2025
          Color: GraphiteVerified Purchase
          For context my main headphones are HD600, oppo pm-3, and some Koss kph-40, Ive also owned some extremely expensive headphones, so Im no newbie when it comes to decent headphones, and I gotta say Im pleasantly surprised by this compact little j-labs.

          First off, build quality is actually really nice, its far better than the jbl and Sony offerings in this price range. A nice leather piece above the fabric headband, and wonderfully soft and comfy ear pads.

          Audio quality is really nice here, I recommend downloading the app, going to EQ and dropping all the sliders to the very bottom then just tweaking things ever so slightly to your liking. Out of the box they sound pretty bad, and j-labs personal eq profile in my opinion doesnt bring these headphones up to their full potential. Instruments are very well separated, nothing is muddy, everything sounds clean and natural, Im genuinely impressed, and the more time I spend with them the more I enjoy them. They work with all genres and are surprisingly capable little beasts. They have 40mm drivers like a sennheiser hd598, so dont be fooled by their small form factor.

          Comfort is a big win here too, I can wear these for hours with no fatigue on my ears, the headband can dig in ever so slightly but thats more of a me thing as all headphones cause me the same issue on the top of my head.

          Ive bought these for the gym as they have anc and a transparency mode, and the anc is genuinely GOOD. It does a fantastic job and quieting down all sounds, nothing just low sounds of vehicles and airplanes, but also clattering of dumbbells and footsteps.

          Battery life is PHENOMENAL, 70 hours without anc, 40 with anc on.

          Overall I hugely recommend these headphones , theyre fantastic, and have given me real confidence in the American j-lab brand.

          At this price point for this spec I think theyre unbeatable.

        About this Item

        • Hybrid ANC and Be Aware Mode: Hybrid Active Noise Cancelation leverages mics on the exterior and interior of the headphone for optimal noise cancelation performance across a broad frequency range. Activate the Hybrid Active Noise Canceling to eliminate external distractions up to 30 dB or switch to Be Aware mode to remain connected to your environment.
        • Cloud Foam Comfort: Form-Fit Earcups are ergonomically shaped to the natural outline of the ear. The 1 Cloud Foam cushions and adjustable hinges further customize your comfort for any travel, workout, or commute.
        • Customize Your Sound + Experience via JLab App: With the new JLab App, customize the ANC/Be Aware settings, touch controls, and sound to your personal preference - or use the presets for JLab Signature, Balance or Bass Boost. Safe hearing option allows you to protect your ears from hearing damage with volume limits. Plus, get software updates for your product right when they're available. Available on the App Store or Google Play Store.
        • Crystal Clear Calls: Furnished with cutting-edge noise-canceling microphones, these headphones ensure crystal clear and uninterrupted communication during calls, ensuring exceptional clarity and eliminating external disturbances for an impeccable conversation experience.
        • Easy Connections + Google Find My: Utilize Bluetooth Multipoint to seamlessly connect to and toggle between two devices simultaneously for added convenience. Wireless Share Mode allows you to share audio wirelessly between two Lux headphones.
        • Easy Connections: Utilize Bluetooth Multipoint to seamlessly connect to and toggle between two devices simultaneously for added convenience. Wireless Share Mode allows you to share audio wirelessly between two Lux headphones. Plus effortless pairing with an Android device with Google Fast Pair and Microsoft Swift Pair. When you take out your headphones and have a supported Android device, youll see a pop-up enabling you to connect via Bluetooth. With Microsoft Swift Pair, seamlessly connect to Microsoft Windows 10 and 11 devices. When a Windows 10 or 11 PC detects the Go Lux ANC it will prompt you to connect with a single click.
        • Google Find My Device: With Google Find My Device, you can locate your headphones.
        • Includes: Headphones, Charging Cable, JLab 2 Year Warranty

        Product Description

        Experience luxurious sound with Go Lux ANC Headphones a new benchmark in audio excellence for on-ear wireless headphones. These sleek and compact headphones seamlessly blend innovation and Lab-quality sound, ensuring an immersive audio experience. Whether you're a city commuter or Zen seeker, Hybrid Active Noise Canceling and personalized sound customization via the JLab App produce an audio sanctuary. Indulge in your favorite tunes or podcasts in ultimate comfort and style with Cloud Foam earcups and headband, ensuring a listening experience that's worth every penny. Hybrid ANC and Be Aware Mode Hybrid Active Noise Cancelation leverages mics on the exterior and interior of the headphone for optimal noise cancelation performance across a broad frequency range. Activate the Hybrid Active Noise Canceling to eliminate external distractions up to 30 dB or switch to Be Aware mode to remain connected to your environment. Cloud Foam Comfort Form-Fit Earcups are ergonomically shaped to the natural outline of the ear. The 1 Cloud Foam cushions and adjustable hinges further customize your comfort for any travel, workout, or commute. Customize Your Sound + Experience via JLab App With the new JLab App, customize the ANC/Be Aware settings, touch controls, and sound to your personal preference - or use the presets for JLab Signature, Balance or Bass Boost. Safe hearing option allows you to protect your ears from hearing damage with volume limits. Plus, get software updates for your product right when they're available. Available on the App Store or Google Play Store. Crystal Clear Calls Furnished with cutting-edge noise-canceling microphones, these headphones ensure crystal clear and uninterrupted communication during calls, ensuring exceptional clarity and eliminating external disturbances for an impeccable conversation experience. Easy Connections + Google Find My Utilize Bluetooth Multipoint to seamlessly connect to and toggle between two devices simultaneously for added convenience. Wireless Share Mode allows you to share audio wirelessly between two Lux headphones. Plus effortless pairing with an Android device with Google Fast Pair and Microsoft Swift Pair. When you take out your headphones and have a supported Android device, youll see a pop-up enabling you to connect via Bluetooth. Dont worry if youre not an Android user, JLab earbuds will connect with any Bluetooth enabled device like iPhone with just a couple taps. Plus with Google Find My Device, you can locate your headphones. With Microsoft Swift Pair, seamlessly connect to Microsoft Windows 10 and 11 devices. When a Windows 10 or 11 PC detects the Go Lux ANC it will prompt you to connect with a single click.
